OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading this evening, leaving a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping across the region. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly under clear skies, especially
OL,10,Fin the countryside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry and sunny start, but
OL,13,Fcloud will tend to increase throughout
OL,14,Fthe day, with a scattering of showers
OL,15,Fdeveloping. Showers potentially
OL,16,Fturning heavier into the afternoon.
OL,17,FFeeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
