OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,6,Fbright day on Sunday but feeling much
OL,7,Fcooler. Remaining cool early next with
OL,8,Ffurther showers or longer spells of
OL,9,Frain, but also some drier and sunnier
OL,10,Finterludes.
